event.title: Baddie Ballers
event.description:
Baddie Ballers: Where Beauty Meets Game

Get ready for the ultimate fusion of glam and game at Baddie Ballers — a high-energy basketball showdown where fierce style meets fierce competition. Whether you're here to play or slay, this event is all about confidence, culture, and community. Expect music, fashion, highlight-worthy plays, and vibes that don’t quit.
